      <title>烏克蘭哈爾科夫州州長稱俄羅斯襲擊造成六人受傷</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russian-attack-injures-six-people-ukraines-kharkiv-governor-says-2024-04-24/</link>
